2. **HLint code actions** - Applying hlint suggestions via quickfix

## Documentation and Search
3. **Hoogle online search** - Search Hoogle database for functions
4. **Hoogle lookup at point** - Look up identifier under cursor in Hoogle
5. **Hoogle local database** - Generate and use offline Hoogle database
6. **Hoogle project-specific search** - Scope Hoogle to project dependencies
7. **Hoogle import insertion** - Use Hoogle to identify and add missing imports
8. **View Haddock documentation** - Display Haddock docs for symbols
9. **Generate Haddock comments** - Create Haddock comment skeletons

## Program Synthesis
10. **Djinn synthesis** - Synthesize function implementations from type signatures
11. **Djinn at point** - Invoke Djinn on type signature at cursor
12. **MagicHaskeller search** - Synthesize implementations from examples
13. **Hoogle+ synthesis** - Program synthesis from types and examples

## Testing and Property Generation
14. **QuickSpec property generation** - Auto-discover algebraic properties
15. **Spectacular test generation** - Generate QuickCheck tests from signatures
16. **Run test suite** - Execute project tests and display results

## Import Management
17. **Organize imports** - Sort, group, and remove unused imports
18. **Qualify imports** - Convert regular imports to qualified imports

## Code Editing
